      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON FRANKY (1) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on his swift win the start prior, getting around this track over 400m in 23.24. Can measure up on top win two back. LUST TO BURN (2) charged out of the boxes with a strong early split and went straight to the front, scoring an all the way win (23.30) over 400m at this track. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. JAJA DING DONG (7) finds it hard to break through. Finished second (23.46) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Will give a great sight again. COMPTON TIG (4) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.",
